[IMG]http://i369.photobucket.com/albums/oo131/0xXDylanXx0/dksrs.jpg[/img]

item.title: [RELEASE]Dark Knight Sword[/RELEASE] - Now RS Capable
item.dc:creator: @dylan_0789 dylan_0789
item.description:
@dylan_0789 wrote:

[quote=“time of rune, post:14, topic:295201”]I honestly can’t say I’ve even disliked any of your models dylan. 1 suggestion to low-poly models that are intended for RSPS, if the blade is going to have those cuts into it, make it a bit more prominent(can’t spell), because as you can see in the pic above, the cuts barely seem noticable.

Thanks :)[/quote]

i agree completely, but remember, origionally, this wasnt intended to be a low poly RS model, i had to remove 13,000 faces. the reason the pummel and hilt are semi-plain is because i was going for a more traditional look with a touch of fantasy sword looks, as people always tell me the blades werent fancy enough and the hilt was overly-fancy.
